name: orange3-survival-analysis
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "Orange3-Survival-Analysis" %}
{% set version = "0.3.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e0459e90c8e9687ebb497d36df194f8476ea4d36dc1bbbd1201bf43fba41cf7b

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - Orange3
    - lifelines

test:
  imports:
    - orangecontrib.survival_analysis

about:
  home: http://orange.biolab.si/
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Survival Analysis add-on for Orange3 data mining suite
  description: |
    Orange3 Survival Analysis add-on for the Orange3 data mining suite.
  # todo: add when available: doc_url
  dev_url: https://github.com/biolab/orange3-survival-analysis

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - primozgodec
    - markotoplak
    - JakaKokosar
